channel.title: How to get a server online
channel.description:
Hey I have my server, I have done some to it, and I have done all the portforwarding and stuff. I have a no-ip. So what I'm wondering is how do I get it online so that other people can play it too? If you can help, please post. Thanks!
PS. I have done the tutorial.
I guess what I'm trying to say is how do I connect my no-ip to my server? I have my no-ip up and I have a check mark by my server.
